room_title: Escape room "Arcade" by Portland Escape Rooms in Portland
room_address: 10700 SW Beaverton-Hillsdale Hwy, Suite 118 Beaverton OR 97005
room_description: You are trapped in an arcade where the crazy arcade owner has decided to play a game with you. A bomb with a timer is set to go off in 60 minutes unless your team can solve the puzzles to get out before it explodes. You can try for the high score, but in this game, you only get one life!
